# Database Standards

Follow the canonical standards: **`.ai/standards/postgresql.md`** and **`.ai/standards/mysql.md`**

Key rules:
- Reversible migrations when possible
- Index all foreign keys
- Large table DDL requires online schema change strategy

Agent: `.ai/agents/rails-architect.yaml` (data modeling, migrations, indexing)  
Skills: `review-db-migrations`, `sql-review`
